5|$|By the 1980s, Galland was now {{regularly}} attending <b>the</b> <b>funerals</b> {{of friends}} like Tuck, and also Douglas Bader, {{who had died}} on 5 September 1982 after speaking at a dinner for Arthur Harris. In June 1983 he attended the funeral of Gerhard Barkhorn and his wife Christl, {{who had died in}} a traffic accident.|$|E
